{"word":"ἀδείμαντος","slug":"ἀδείμαντος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀδείμαντος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:δειμαίνω'><el>δειμαίνω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>fearless, dauntless</i>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>:—<a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>-τως</el>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>where no fear is</i>, <el>οἰκία</el> <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}